Interface ChartData<P extends Plot>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - Type of Plot object
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BarTimeChartData<P>, PeriodChartData<P>, PieChartData<P>, PieTimeChartData<P>, ScatterPeriodChartData<P>, TimeChartData<P>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JFreeBarTimeChartData, JFreeChart3DPieChartData, JFreeChartData, JFreePieChartData, JFreeScatterPeriodChartData, JFreeTimeChartData

    public interface ChartData<P extends Plot>
    Interface for objects that represent the actual Chart graphic Objects implementing this interface are intended to be the graphic-library internal implementation of chart objects.
